The category of Phases One and Three of this proceeding is quasi-legislative; Phase Two is categorized as ratesetting. An evidentiary hearing is not necessary at this time, but may be needed at a later date. The scope of the issues and the schedule for this proceeding are as set forth. Ex parte communications are permitted without restriction or reporting for Phase One and Three of this proceeding. With limited exceptions that are subject to reporting requirements, ex parte communications are prohibited in Phase Two of this proceeding.  In Phase Two of this proceeding, Administrative Law Judge Kelly A. Hymes is designated as the Presiding Officer.
